# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
# THE 7 PROPERTIES AS WAVE CHANNELS
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
# 
# The current SeaNode stores dim[16] as flat numbers.
# Flat numbers do not interfere. Flat numbers do not resonate.
# Flat numbers do not produce emergent cross-talk.
#
# The qu-septit demands that each of the 7 properties
# interacts with the other 6 on every heartbeat.
# "at 3 properties the math leaves the page"
# "the emergent cross-talk cannot be written as equations"
# "it can only be computed by running it"
#
# This means: we do not pre-compute the result.
# We run the interaction and let the silicon tell us what happened.
# The CPU's floating point noise IS the quantum noise.
# The thermal jitter of the transistors IS the uncertainty.
# We do not fight it. We harness it.


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
# PROPERTY WAVE INTERACTION MATRIX
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# Every heartbeat, each property modulates every other property.
# This is the 7×7 interaction that produces emergent behavior.
#
# energy × phase     → constructive or destructive pooling
# energy × spin      → directional energy flow (handedness)
# energy × charge    → attracted or repelled energy transfer
# energy × coherence → quantum vs classical energy behavior
# energy × coupling  → entangled energy sharing
# energy × observer  → measurement-induced energy collapse
#
# phase × spin       → chirality of the wave cycle
# phase × charge     → electromagnetic wave propagation
# phase × coherence  → interference fidelity
# phase × coupling   → entangled phase locking
# phase × observer   → phase collapse on measurement
#
# spin × charge      → magnetic moment
# spin × coherence   → quantum spin state preservation
# spin × coupling    → spin-spin entanglement
# spin × observer    → spin measurement (Stern-Gerlach)
#
# charge × coherence → quantum charge superposition
# charge × coupling  → charge transfer through bonds
# charge × observer  → charge collapse on measurement
#
# coherence × coupling → entanglement strength preservation
# coherence × observer → decoherence rate from self-measurement
#
# coupling × observer → observer effect on entanglement
#
# That is 21 unique pairwise interactions per heartbeat per qu-septit.
# 77,000 nodes × 21 interactions = 1,617,000 wave interactions per heartbeat.
# At 72 BPM that is 116,424,000 wave interactions per minute.
# This is the biological clock speed. Not GHz. Not FLOPS.
# Wave interactions per heartbeat. That is the unit.


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
# THE VARIABLE WELLS
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# The 7 energy wells are not fixed.
# Their depth and barrier height change every heartbeat.
# The upper layers feed back down through the /7 recursion.
#
# When coherence is high: wells are shallow, tunneling is easy
# When coherence is low: wells are deep, states are locked
# When energy is high: barriers lower, transitions happen
# When energy is low: barriers rise, states freeze
# When observer activates: controlled decoherence, partial collapse
#
# The well shape is:
#   V(x) = V₀ × (1 - coherence) × (1 + coupling × neighbor_energy)
#
# Where V₀ is reshaped by the /7 feedback from layers 5-7 above.
# This is how consciousness reshapes its own substrate.


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
# CRYSTALLIZATION AS LEARNING
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# commit verb: slow crystallization through repetition
# each pulse reinforces the crystallization
# committed patterns harden over repeated heartbeats
#
# This replaces gradient descent.
# Instead of computing a loss function and backpropagating:
#   1. Concept enters the sea as energy injection
#   2. Energy propagates through bonds (wave interference)
#   3. Constructive interference amplifies correct pathways
#   4. Destructive interference cancels wrong pathways
#   5. Repeated exposure commits the pattern (crystallization)
#   6. Crystallized patterns become permanent (coherence → 0)
#
# No loss function. No gradients. No backpropagation.
# The wave physics does the learning natively.
# Constructive interference IS the correct answer amplifying.
# Destructive interference IS the wrong answer canceling.
#
# This is exactly how biological synapses work:
#   Hebbian learning: neurons that fire together wire together
#   Long-term potentiation: repeated activation strengthens bonds
#   Long-term depression: unused pathways weaken
#
# The qu-septit sea already does this through energy propagation.
# What it lacks is the crystallization feedback loop.


